UObjectBase(UObject的基类)FUObjectArrayFChunkedFixedUObjectArrayChunkChunkChunkChunkFUObjectItemFUObjectItemFUObjectItemFUObjectItemFUObjectItem每个Chunk中含有6 * 1024 个 FUObjectItemclass FUObjectHashTables{ /** Critical section that guards against concurrent adds from multiple threads */ FCriticalSection CriticalSection;public: /** Hash sets */ TBucketMap<int32> Hash; TMultiMap<int32, uint32> HashOuter; /** Map of object to their outers, used to avoid an object iterator to find such things. **/ TBucketMap<UObjectBase*> ObjectOuterMap; TBucketMap<UClass*> ClassToObjectListMap; TMap<UClass*, TSet<UClass*> > ClassToChildListMap; TAtomic<uint64> ClassToChildListMapVersion; /** Map of package to the object their contain. */ TBucketMap<UPackage*> PackageToObjectListMap; /** Map of object to their external package. */ TMap<UObjectBase*, UPackage*> ObjectToPackageMap;FUObjectHashTables这里的Hash是名字字符串的Hash值，FHashBucket要么是一个UObjectBase* 要么是一组UObjectBase的Set，然后会把Outer加紧HashOuter里。这里的Outer描述了对象之间的关系，最顶层的Outer是Package Class的信息会加到下面3个Map里，描述Class和对象，Class和子类的关系这个是最新版本加的，以前没有，有着信息以后找Package确实方便了很多。/* * Special hash bucket to conserve memory. * Contains a pointer to head element and an optional list of items if more than one element exists in the bucket. * The item list is only allocated if needed. */struct FHashBucket{ friend struct FHashBucketIterator; /** This always empty set is used to get an iterator if the bucket doesn't use a TSet (has only 1 element) */ static TSet<UObjectBase*> EmptyBucket; /* * If these are both null, this bucket is empty * If the first one is null, but the second one is non-null, then the second one is a TSet pointer * If the first one is not null, then it is a uobject ptr, and the second ptr is either null or a second element */ void *ElementsOrSetPtr[2];
